collection.name: Extension Loot (for Adventurers)
collection.description: Extension Loot is second set of Loot, a randomized adventurer gear generated and stored on chain. It uses the same algo as Loot, Extension Loot is just more Loot. Stats, images, and other functionality are intentionally omitted for others to interpret. Feel free to use Exension Loot in any way you want.
